{"tid":576063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(發呆比賽) 方力申張繼聰tag 人鬥發夢　全城挑戰發呆1分鐘","createTime":"2018-02-28T15:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T15:11:00.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62be2517912f8268bac30f538ae1594216163a76","tid":576063,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"之前14年網上見韓國搞發呆比賽，成班人坐喺草地度發呆，成個畫面非常搞笑，網民個個都好有自信話如果香港搞呢個比賽實贏梗。機會嚟喇飛雲，第6屆發呆比賽嚟到香港站，喺3月31號舉行，目的就係想大家輕鬆一下，關注都市情緒病，香港地人人壓力大，根據統計話每六個港人就有一位會患上情緒病，所以得閒冇事發吓呆，冇咁容易鬱到病。<br />\n<br />\n專頁分別喺Facebook同Instagram就發起咗個叫「全城挑戰發呆1分鐘」嘅Tag，叫大家拍低發呆嘅1分鐘短片，自己要完全唔受外界影響嘅，之後再Tag 3個你覺得好需要發呆紓壓嘅朋友。藝人方力申身先士卒支持，仲Tag咗老友洪天明、張繼聰同蘇麗珊，真係相當搞鬼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/230440_be5e11caeae8aa9a9c2e4b6908c78299.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F230440_be5e11caeae8aa9a9c2e4b6908c78299.jpg&h=e1d68afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/230443_897d9a124261403ce86c713cff9ba49c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F230443_897d9a124261403ce86c713cff9ba49c.jpg&h=97fd2f3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/230447_f7e63f448f3d75d5f325bc1b9dfd1a9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F230447_f7e63f448f3d75d5f325bc1b9dfd1a9d.jpg&h=eb995fb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cf41f0b8d18454245299273ca85d144b1abdff9","tid":576063,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"諗起貝夫人"},{"pid":"dbbfd0804e949b7b1656afb9628246da054c7578","tid":576063,"uid":105552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"上面個兩條友咩料<br />\n馬國明個啲先叫發呆囉好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}